videos.description: Nick Saban says there is a lot to learn for Alabama and makes it clear he wasn't pleased with his team's intensity or defense in the second half.
videos.headline: Saban displeased with Bama's second-half intensity

videos.description: Crimson Tide QB Mac Jones says the atmosphere was weird to play in but adds that it didn't affect his comfort level.
videos.headline: Mac Jones: 'I was pretty comfortable'

videos.description: No. 2 Alabama gets a blowout win over Mizzou 38-19, with three rushing touchdowns from Najee Harris.
videos.headline: Harris' three scores lead Tide to Week 1 win
